Book.java       - Class represents a book
Library.java    - Class represents the library
Patron.java     - Class represents a patron



=============================
=          Design           =
=============================
In library class I made an array of books, that contains all the book in the library, moreover I
 made an array of patrons that save all patrons in library.



=============================
=  Implementation details   =
=============================
In library class i chose to save books and patrons in arrays because of the easy of inserting and deleting
 items.



